data.description: Charming 2-story in coveted downtown Valparaiso! Walk to concerts, festivals, & shops. Lovingly maintained w/original woodwork, doorknobs, & built-ins throughout. Foyer welcomes you w/ gorgeous wood staircase & coat closet. Arched entry leads to oversized living room w/great natural lighting. Formal dining room with backyard views, built-ins, &classic swinging door to kitchen. Kitchen offers original ceiling-height cabinets, built-in storage, & breakfast nook w/sliding door to back deck. Main level owner's suite offers laundry, sitting area, plus ensuite bath w/ step-in shower. Upstairs, retreat to 3 additional bedrooms w/ original hardwood floors, built-in storage, built-in desk, a walk-in closet, & easy access to full hallway bath. Basement boasts rec room (potential 5th bed), loads of storage space, & canning room. Back yard flower garden is a peaceful oasis from your busy life & 2-car garage is perfect for cars, tools, & toys! Home offers a 2018 roof, a whole house fan & generator!
